'''韓流'''，是指[[韩国文化|韩国文化]]在[[亚洲|亚洲]]和[[世界|世界]]范围内流行的现象<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/herald/2011-07/29/c_131015358.htm|title=“韩流”旋风登陆欧美|publisher=新华网|accessdate=2014-10-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303041211/http://news.xinhuanet.com/herald/2011-07/29/c_131015358.htm|archivedate=2016-03-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://theory.people.com.cn/BIG5/n/2014/0315/c40531-24642937.html |title = “韓流”為何能在中國一火再火 |publisher = 中国共产党新闻网 |accessdate = 2014-10-19 |archive-date = 2014-10-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141026005451/http://theory.people.com.cn/BIG5/n/2014/0315/c40531-24642937.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://news.ifeng.com/gundong/detail_2012_10/30/18660553_0.shtml |title = 媒体称韩国政府是韩流背后最强大推手 |publisher = 凤凰网 |accessdate = 2014-10-19 |archive-date = 2016-03-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160319023256/http://news.ifeng.com/gundong/detail_2012_10/30/18660553_0.shtml |dead-url = no }}</ref>。韩流一般以[[韩国电影|韩国电影]]、[[韩剧|电视剧]]为代表，与[[韩国流行乐|韩国音乐]]、[[图书|图书]]、[[大韩民国#網路遊戲|电子游戏]]、[[服饰|服饰]]、[[韩国料理|饮食]]、[[韩国体育|体育]]、[[韩国旅游业|旅游观光]]、化妆美容、[[韩语|韩语]]等形成一个彼此影响和带动的循环体系，因而具有极为强大的流行力量<ref>{{cite web |url =http://ocm.wenweipo.com/newsdb/news/2012-08-20/9365.html |title =韩流在华成功20年，期待实现可持续发展 |publisher =海外华文传媒合作组织 |accessdate =2014-10-19 |deadurl =yes |archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20141019090440/http://ocm.wenweipo.com/newsdb/news/2012-08-20/9365.html |archivedate =2014-10-19 }}</ref>。

“韩流”一词最初为[[中文|中文]]媒体所提出{{r|hanliu1|page=1}}，用來形容[[男孩團體|男孩團體]][[H.O.T.|H.O.T.]]帶到中國的韓國潮流<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.munhwa.com/news/view.html?no=2016011901033011000001|title=‘H.O.T’ 데뷔 20년|date=2016-01-19|website=[[文化日報|文化日報]]|access-date=2018-04-20|archive-date=2018-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180421030821/http://www.munhwa.com/news/view.html?no=2016011901033011000001|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.munhwa.com/news/view.html?no=2012070401033730030002|title=이수만회장의 발걸음 너무 빠르다|date=2012-07-04|website=[[文化日報|文化日報]]|access-date=2018-04-20|archive-date=2018-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180421030603/http://www.munhwa.com/news/view.html?no=2012070401033730030002|dead-url=no}}</ref>。后来被[[韩国|韩国]]媒体广泛用于指代本国文化产业的输出<ref name=huabian>{{cite web |url = http://www.huabian.com/dapian/2013/0926/2509.html |title = 韩流入侵好莱坞电影产业韩裔明星总演日本人 |publisher = 花边星闻 |accessdate = 2014-10-19 |archive-date = 2014-01-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140108021133/http://www.huabian.com/dapian/2013/0926/2509.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cien.com.cn/html/Home/report/86039-1.htm|title=韩流文化|publisher=产经新闻网|accessdate=2014-10-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923203405/http://www.cien.com.cn/html/Home/report/86039-1.htm|archivedate=2015-09-23}}</ref>。“Hallyu”已经在英语中被用来指代“韩流”<ref name=huabian />。韩流在世界范围的流行使韩国[[软实力|软实力]]世界排名和国家形象得到提高<ref>{{cite web |title=2012 BBC Country  Ratings |url=http://www.globescan.com/images/images/pressreleases/bbc2012_country_ratings/2012_bbc_country%20rating%20final%20080512.pdf |publisher=Globescan/BBC World Service |accessdate=2012-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130421045246/http://www.globescan.com/images/images/pressreleases/bbc2012_country_ratings/2012_bbc_country%20rating%20final%20080512.pdf |archive-date=2013-04-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2012/11/20/2012112000616.html Korea Ranks 11th in Global Soft Power] {{Wayback|url=http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2012/11/20/2012112000616.html |date=20141120013859 }}, The Chosun Ilbo</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Hallyu seeks sustainability |url=http://nwww.koreaherald.com/common_prog/newsprint.php?ud=20130212001037&dt=2 |publisher=The Korea Herald |accessdate=2013-03-21 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6FHqPkNDz?url=http://nwww.koreaherald.com/common_prog/newsprint.php?ud=20130212001037 |archivedate=2013-03-21 |quote=According to the Hallyu Future Strategy Forum's 2012 report, hallyu was worth 5.6 trillion won in economic value and 95 trillion won in asset value. |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，韩流作为文化产业得到韩国政府的扶植<ref>{{cite web |url = http://news.ifeng.com/world/detail_2013_11/18/31346851_0.shtml |title = 韩国政府将投资逾5万亿扶植“韩流”文化产业 |publisher = 凤凰网 |accessdate = 2014-10-26 |archive-date = 2014-10-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141026080742/http://news.ifeng.com/world/detail_2013_11/18/31346851_0.shtml |dead-url = no }}</ref>。韩国政府期望通过韩流的发展，促进韩国文化在外国的推广，消除部分外国人的[[反韩情绪|反韩情绪]]<ref name="antikoreansentiment">{{cite web |title=Korea to turn hallyu into industry |url=http://nwww.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20120417001073 |publisher=The Korea Herald |accessdate=17 February 2013 |quote=To prevent anti-Korean sentiment, the government will offer incentives for production companies or broadcasters planning to jointly produce movies or dramas with Chinese companies. |archive-date=2015-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703132054/http://nwww.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20120417001073 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，促进[[朝鮮半島統一問題|朝鲜半岛的统一]]<ref name="reutershallyu">{{cite news |title="Korean Wave" set to swamp North Korea, academics say |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/29/us-media-northkorea-idUSTRE73S5J420110429 |publisher=Reuters |accessdate=2013-03-18 |date=2011-04-29 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924152707/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/29/us-media-northkorea-idUSTRE73S5J420110429 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和推动世界和平与繁荣<ref name="wp">{{cite web |title = 'Hallyu could be a stepping stone for peace' |url = http://nwww.koreaherald.com/common_prog/newsprint.php?ud=20130212001036&dt=2 |publisher = The Korea Herald |accessdate = 2013-04-30 |archive-date = 2013-03-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130325061204/http://nwww.koreaherald.com/common_prog/newsprint.php?ud=20130212001036&dt=2 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 发展史 ==
===历史背景===
1962年，[[朴正熙|朴正熙]]发动政变上台后逐步实行遏制电影业发展的政策。在军人独裁下的韩国，电影业发展低迷。这段时期被称为韩国电影业“失去的二十年”<ref name="原因">{{cite web  |url =http://culture.163.com/06/0302/16/2B7LIFMB00281MU3.html  |title =韩国电影崛起的原因  |publisher =网易  |accessdate =2014-10-09  |archive-date =2014-10-17  |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20141017113048/http://culture.163.com/06/0302/16/2B7LIFMB00281MU3.html  |dead-url =no  }}</ref>。1987年[[六月民主運動|六月民主運動]]後，随着军人独裁统治在韩国的终结，[[韩国电影|韩国电影]]业开始复苏。不过这一时期的韩国电影业主要由成产空白[[录像带|录像带]]、[[VCR|VCR]]的[[韩国财阀|韩国财阀]]控制。这些财阀制作电影的目的其实就是为了销售他们的录像带、VCR而非[[电影|电影]]本身{{r|原因}}。韩国对国外电影采取{{le|影视配额|screen quotas}}制度限制外国电影准入的数量<ref>{{cite news|title=South Korea: The king, the clown and the quota|url=http://www.economist.com/node/5531891|publisher=The Economist|accessdate=17 March 2013|date=18 February 2006|archive-date=2014-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141104174535/http://www.economist.com/node/5531891|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当时的韩国电影产业不足以筹集大量资金出品高成本的电影，这一政策有利于保护本国电影业免收外国[[大片|大片]]的冲击<ref>{{cite web|title=The Future, after the Screen Quota|url=http://www.knutimes.com/news/article.html?no=564|publisher=The KNU Times|accessdate=8 April 2013|archive-date=2014-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141104140055/http://www.knutimes.com/news/article.html?no=564|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

1986年，[[美国电影协会|美国电影协会]]向美国参议院提交一份抗议，旨在抗议韩国政府对外国电影的“不公平”政策<ref>{{cite book|last=Lee|first=Hyung-Sook|title=Between Local and Global: The Hong Kong Film Syndrome in South Korea|year=2006|publisher=ProQuest|page=48}}</ref>。鑒于美国联邦政府的施压，韩国政府逐渐放宽对美国好莱坞电影的准入。1988年，[[二十世纪福克斯|二十世纪福克斯]]成为首个在韩国设立办事处的美国电影公司，之后[[华纳兄弟|华纳兄弟]]、[[哥伦比亚电影公司|哥伦比亚电影公司]]、[[迪士尼电影公司|迪士尼电影公司]]纷纷进入韩国<ref>{{cite book|last=Choi|first=Jinhee|title=The South Korean Film Renaissance: Local Hitmakers, Global Provocateurs|url=https://archive.org/details/southkoreanfilmr00choi|year=2010|publisher=Wesleyan University Press|pages=[https://archive.org/details/southkoreanfilmr00choi/page/n28 16]}}</ref>。

=== 1994年–1999年：初期开始 ===
1994年，在[[韩国电影|韩国电影]]市场上，好莱坞所占有的份额已经达到80%，而韩国本国的电影份额却只有15.9%<ref>[http://nwww.koreaherald.com/common_prog/newsprint.php?ud=20120917000815&dt=2 What is the future of Korean film?] {{Wayback|url=http://nwww.koreaherald.com/common_prog/newsprint.php?ud=20120917000815&dt=2 |date=20140106130235 }}, ''The Korea Herald''</ref>。同年，韩国总统[[金泳三|金泳三]]展示了一份总统顾问委员会的报告，其中建议支持和资助韩国的文化与传媒产业，并将其当做国家的战略出口产业<ref>{{cite web|last=ROUSSE-MARQUET|first=Jennifer|title=K-pop : the story of the well-oiled industry of standardized catchy tunes|url=http://www.inaglobal.fr/en/music/article/k-pop-story-well-oiled-industry-standardized-catchy-tunes|accessdate=17 March 2013|archive-date=2014-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701232206/http://www.inaglobal.fr/en/music/article/k-pop-story-well-oiled-industry-standardized-catchy-tunes|dead-url=yes}}</ref>；随后，[[韩国文化体育观光部|韩国文化体育观光部]]设立文化产业局以推动文化产业发展<ref name="shim">{{cite web|last=Shim|first=Doobo|title=Waxing the Korean Wave|url=http://www.ari.nus.edu.sg/docs/wps/wps11_158.pdf|publisher=National University of Singapore|accessdate=17 March 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120417033941/http://www.ari.nus.edu.sg/docs/wps/wps11_158.pdf|archivedate=2012年4月17日}}</ref>。1997年，受[[亚洲金融危机|亚洲金融危机]]影响，[[韩国财阀|韩国财阀]]从传媒和娱乐产业退出，大批以[[好莱坞|好莱坞]]模式营运得独立制片公司如雨后春笋般涌现出来<ref>{{cite book|last=Huat|first=Chua Beng|title=East Asian pop culture|year=2008|publisher=Hong Kong University press|location=Hong Kong|isbn=9789622098923|url=http://hongkong.universitypressscholarship.com/view/10.5790/hongkong/9789622098923.001.0001/upso-9789622098923-chapter-2?rskey=FViWWg&result=5&q=economy|author2=Iwabuchi, Koichi|access-date=2014-10-21|archive-date=2014-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106145755/http://hongkong.universitypressscholarship.com/view/10.5790/hongkong/9789622098923.001.0001/upso-9789622098923-chapter-2?rskey=FViWWg&result=5&q=economy|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1993年，韩国电影之父[[林权泽|林权泽]]导演的《[[西便制|西便制]]》打开了韩国电影100万观众的新纪元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://wuxizazhi.cnki.net/Article/DYLX201014034.html|title=解读韩国传统文化艺术之精华《西便制》|publisher=吾喜杂志|accessdate=2014-11-10|archive-date=2014-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110132221/http://wuxizazhi.cnki.net/Article/DYLX201014034.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1999年，韩国著名导演[[姜帝圭|姜帝圭]]自编自导的韩国第一部本土大片《[[生死谍变|生死谍变]]》取得巨大成功，票房收入超过1000万美元<ref>{{cite news|last=MACINTYRE|first=DONALD|title=Korea's Big Moment|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,173502,00.html|publisher=''Time''|accessdate=2013-05-17|quote=Technical quality improved steadily and genres multiplied. Shiri, released in 1999, was the breakthrough. Hollywood-style in its pacing and punch, it probed the still-sensitive issue of relations between the two Koreas through the story of a North Korean assassin who falls in love with a South Korean counterintelligence agent. The film sold 5.8 million tickets, shattering the previous record for a locally made movie of 1 million. Its $11 million box office grabbed the attention of investors, who are clamoring for new projects.|date=2001-09-10|archive-date=2013-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130525190213/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,173502,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，票房人数达到660万，打破了1997年《泰坦尼克号》在韩国创下的417万人次记录。这是韩国电影第一次打败[[好莱坞电影|好莱坞电影]]，使韩国人对本土电影的信心陡然激增<ref name="原因"/>。

[[韩国电影|韩国电影]]业的兴起也带动了[[韩剧|韩剧]]的兴起。[[韩国文化|韩国文化]]的向外输出开始于[[韩剧|韩剧]]在[[中国|中国]]的热播。1997年，中央电视台在第八套影视频道播出电视剧《[[爱情是什么|爱情是什么]]》，在中国观众引起轰动，收视率高达4.2%{{r|hanliu1|page=1-2}}。同年，韩国宇田公司为代表将大量韩国音乐人作品介绍到中国，韩国作品遂如雨后春笋。这个时期主要是电视剧与音乐为主，特別是偶像組合[[H.O.T.|H.O.T.]]在[[北京|北京]]舉行演唱會的高人氣<ref>{{cite web|title=韩媒称"韩流"在中国遇阻:欲走"高端路线"求质变|url=http://news.haiwainet.cn/n/2017/0827/c3541083-31088566.html|publisher=[[人民日報|人民日報]]|date=2017-08-27|accessdate=2018-04-20|archive-date=2018-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180421030632/http://news.haiwainet.cn/n/2017/0827/c3541083-31088566.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，開創了偶像文化、粉絲文化、應援文化<ref>{{cite web|title=「因為是始祖、因為太年輕」沒有H.O.T.沒有今天韓流盛世|url=https://star.ettoday.net/news/1127363|publisher=[[ETtoday新聞雲|ETtoday新聞雲]]|date=2018-03-11|accessdate=2018-03-16|archive-date=2018-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180316084802/https://star.ettoday.net/news/1127363|dead-url=no}}</ref>，受众为青年女性和中学生{{r|hanliu1|page=2}}。“韩流”或“韩风”一词最初其实是由海峡两岸的中文媒体率先开始使用（取其寒流或寒风自北方而来的谐音双关义），例如1999年11月19日，《[[北京青年报|北京青年报]]》以“韩流”一词描述突显的韩国文化影响力<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fawan.com.cn/html/2012-08/30/content_385806.htm|title=“韩流”影响年轻人|publisher=法制晚报|accessdate=2014-10-19}}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，为应对激增的韩国进口文化产品，中国[[国家广播电影电视总局|国家广播电影电视总局]]开始限制[[韩剧|韩剧]]在中国电视台的播放数量。<ref>[http://www.iias.nl/nl/42/IIAS_NL42_15.pdf When the Korean wave ripples] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iias.nl/nl/42/IIAS_NL42_15.pdf |date=20070614134434 }}, International Institute for Asian Studies</ref>

=== 2000年–2009年：风靡亚洲 ===

进入21世紀后，[[韩剧|韩剧]]和[[韩国流行音乐|韩国流行音乐]]开始在[[亚洲|亚洲]]其它国家和地区逐渐流行。2000年，[[宝儿|宝儿]]签约[[SM娱乐|SM娱乐]]。两年后[[宝儿|宝儿]]的《Listen to My Heart》荣登日本Oricon排行榜首位，成为[[日本|日本]]史上首位拥有百万专辑的韩籍艺人。<ref>{{cite web|title=RIAJ 2002 million-seller list by year|url=http://www.riaj.or.jp/data/others/million_list/2002.html|publisher=RIAJ|accessdate=2014-10-21|archive-date=2008-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080117095925/http://www.riaj.or.jp/data/others/million_list/2002.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2002年，韩剧持续在亚洲升温。《[[蓝色生死恋|蓝色生死恋]]》在[[中国内地|中国内地]]有21个电视频道同时播出。而中国大陆在2002年共播放了316次韩剧，这一纪录远远领先于第二名61次的日剧{{r|hanliu1|page=3}}。在日本，韩剧《[[冬季恋歌|冬季恋歌]]》上映取得巨大成功，相关产品销售额超过350万美元<ref>{{cite web|last=Lee|first=Claire|title=Remembering 'Winter Sonata,' the start of hallyu|url=http://nwww.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20111230000497|publisher=''The Korea Herald''|accessdate=2012-12-26|archive-date=2012-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121226062726/http://nwww.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20111230000497|dead-url=no}}</ref>。时任[[日本首相|日本首相]][[小泉纯一郎|小泉纯一郎]]曾评价说《[[冬季恋歌|冬季恋歌]]》男主角[[裴勇浚|裴勇浚]]在日本的受欢迎度要比他高<ref>{{cite web|last=Lee|first=Claire|title=Remembering 'Winter Sonata,' the start of hallyu|url=http://nwww.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20111230000497|publisher=''The Korea Herald''|accessdate=2012-12-26|quote=The show's popularity in Japan was surprising to many, including the producer Yoon Suk-ho and then-Japanese Prime Minister Junichiro Koizumi, who in 2004 famously said, "Bae Yong-joon is more popular than I am in Japan."|archive-date=2012-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121226062726/http://nwww.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20111230000497|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之后的韩剧比如《[[浪漫满屋|浪漫满屋]]》和《[[大长今|大长今]]》也都取得了同样的成功<ref>{{cite web|last=Lee (이)|first=Hang-soo (항수)|title=홍콩인들 "이영애•송혜교가장좋아"|url=http://news.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2008/08/11/2008081101672.html|work=Chosun Ilbo (in Korean)|accessdate=2013-04-02|archive-date=2014-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221190124/http://news.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2008/08/11/2008081101672.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

随着[[韩剧|韩剧]]的流行，[[韩国流行音乐|韩国流行音乐]]也在[[亚洲|亚洲]]兴起。[[东方神起|东方神起]]、[[SS501|SS501]]和[[Super_Junior|Super Junior]]在这一时期开始走红亚洲<ref>[http://www.allkpop.com/article/2013/02/wbw-sm-vs-dsp "WBW: SM vs. DSP"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.allkpop.com/article/2013/02/wbw-sm-vs-dsp |date=20141021160614 }}.''Allkpop''.Retrieved 2013-07-18.</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Williamson|first=Lucy|title=South Korea's K-pop craze lures fans and makes profits|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/13191346|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2013-03-19|date=2011-04-26|archive-date=2012-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120309151006/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/13191346|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2003年，[[Baby_V.O.X|Baby V.O.X]]的中文单曲「I'm Still Loving You」成功打入中国市场，为韩流在華培养了一大批粉丝。[[Baby_V.O.X|Baby V.O.X]]的韩文单曲「What Should I Do」和中文单曲「I'm Still Loving You」在[[泰国|泰国]]取得同样很好的成绩<ref>{{cite web  |url = http://pipolife.net/more/baby-vox  |title = 歌手介绍 Baby V.O.X  |publisher = PipoLife  |accessdate = 2014-11-01  |deadurl = yes  |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141102071627/http://pipolife.net/more/baby-vox  |archivedate = 2014-11-02  }}</ref>。随后的韩国组合像[[Big_Bang|Big Bang]]和[[Super_Junior|Super Junior]]受到了广大青年人的喜欢，并在开始在[[南美洲|南美洲]]、[[东欧|东欧]]部分地区、[[中东|中东]]和一小部分西方国家地区拥有颇具规模的粉丝。

=== 2009年–2012年：尝试走出亚洲 ===
韩国流行乐在亚洲的走红，诱使一些韩国歌手像[[宝儿|宝儿]]、[[崔东昱|崔东昱]]尝试发行英文歌曲进入西方国家流行音乐市场。但这些尝试最初都不成功。<ref name="nytimeschoe" >{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/05/business/global/using-social-media-to-bring-korean-pop-music-to-the-west.html?pagewanted=all|title=Bringing K-Pop to the West|author=CHOE SANG-HUN and MARK RUSSELL|publisher=2012 The New York Times Company|date=2012-03-04|accessdate=2012-09-12|archive-date=2012-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120322014919/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/05/business/global/using-social-media-to-bring-korean-pop-music-to-the-west.html?pagewanted=all|dead-url=no}}</ref>韩国流行乐在美国只是局限在[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]和[[纽约|纽约]]韩裔人口较多的城市而已。<ref>{{cite news|last=Brown|first=August|title=K-pop enters American pop consciousness|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2012/apr/29/entertainment/la-ca-kpop-20120429/2|publisher=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2013-03-17|date=2012-04-29|archive-date=2013-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130105164619/http://articles.latimes.com/2012/apr/29/entertainment/la-ca-kpop-20120429/2|dead-url=no}}</ref>

不过在北美之外，韩流旋风却很猛。<ref>{{cite web|last=James Russell|first=Mark|title=The Gangnam Phenom|url=http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2012/09/27/the_gangnam_phenom|publisher=''Foreign Policy''|accessdate=2013-03-05|archive-date=2014-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141118112718/http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2012/09/27/the_gangnam_phenom|dead-url=no}}</ref>韩剧《[[朱蒙_(電視劇)|朱蒙]]》在[[穆斯林世界|穆斯林世界]]国家很受欢迎，在[[伊朗|伊朗]]取得超过80%的收视率。<ref name="iranjumong">{{cite web|title=Korea's mark on an expectation-defying Iran|url=http://nwww.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20110810000745|publisher=''The Korea Herald''|accessdate=2013-02-17|quote=The Korean wave, or hallyu, has also made significant forays into Iran. Korean period dramas, "Jumong" in particular, were smash hits. Jumong ― the founding monarch of Korea's ancient Goguryeo kingdom (37 B.C.-A.D. 668) ― has become the most popular TV drama representing Korea here, with its viewer ratings hovering around 80 to 90 percent.|archive-date=2012-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121111103633/http://nwww.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20110810000745|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/middle-east/091216/iran-korea-tv Iranians hooked on Korean TV drama] {{Wayback|url=http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/middle-east/091216/iran-korea-tv |date=20141111094734 }}, ''Global Post''</ref>
2009年的韩剧《[[花樣男子|花樣男子]]》在183个国家播出，被翻译成69种语言，经过了6年仍然持续不断的受到全球影迷的欢迎，人气不减，获第11届（2015）Soompi颁奖典礼韩流特别奖。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://m.allthatstar.com/view.php?action=304&postID=214772 |title=《花样男子》获韩流粉丝肯定 李敏镐发感言意味深长 |accessdate=2016-08-17 |archive-date=2016-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160918175520/http://m.allthatstar.com/view.php?action=304&postID=214772 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>韓星李敏鎬因此與李英愛於2015年榮獲首尔电视节「韓流10年功勞大赏」。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/j/2015-09-11/doc-ifxhupik6714143.shtml |title=首尔电视节落幕 李敏镐李英爱获10年大赏 |accessdate=2016-08-17 |archive-date=2016-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603132335/http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/j/2015-09-11/doc-ifxhupik6714143.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

