==== 伊朗====
[[韩剧|韩剧]]在[[伊朗|伊朗]]收到很高的[[收视率|收视率]]。据《{{Link-en|德黑兰时报|Tehran Times}}》报道，2012年10月1日[[伊朗伊斯兰共和国广播电视台|伊朗伊斯兰共和国广播电视台]]（IRIB）的几位记者还专程来到韩国参观《[[朱蒙_(电视剧)|朱蒙]]》和《[[同伊|同伊]]》等韩剧的拍摄地，<ref name="tehrantimes">[http://www.tehrantimes.com/arts-and-culture/102496-irib-director-visits-location-of-south-korean-tv-series-popular-in-iran- IRIB director visits location of South Korean TV series popular in Iran] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121028100535/http://www.tehrantimes.com/arts-and-culture/102496-irib-director-visits-location-of-south-korean-tv-series-popular-in-iran- |date=2012-10-28 }}, ''The Tehran Times''</ref>并探讨与[[KBS|KBS]]的进一步合作。<ref>{{cite web|title=IRIB director meets South Korean media officials|url=http://english.irib.ir/radioculture/iran/society/media/item/82398-irib-director-meets-south-korean-media-officials|publisher=IRIB World Service|accessdate=2013-04-21|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121027235816/http://english.irib.ir/radioculture/iran/society/media/item/82398-irib-director-meets-south-korean-media-officials|archivedate=2012-10-27}}</ref>

伊朗国家电视台选择在黄金时段播放韩剧的主要原因之一是韩剧宣扬传统[[儒家理念|儒家理念]]，其中许多与[[伊斯兰文化|伊斯兰文化]]很相近，比如社会利益先于个人利益，尊敬上级等。<ref>{{cite web|title= Book probes transnational identity of 'hallyu'|url= http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2013/01/142_91849.html|publisher= ''The Korea Times''|accessdate= 2013-04-22|quote= Korean television dramas reinforce traditional values of Confucianism that Iranians find more closely aligned to Islamic culture, implying that cultural proximity contributes to the Islamic Korean wave. "Reflecting traditional family values, Korean culture is deemed 'a filter for Western values' in Iran," the article says.|archive-date= 2013-12-30|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131230232825/http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/culture/2013/01/142_91849.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>另外由于[[伊朗文化及伊斯兰教令部|伊朗文化及伊斯兰教令部]]对西方影视作品的禁闭，韩剧在伊朗也被用来填补西方影视作品的空缺。<ref name="reutersiran">{{cite news|title=Foreign broadcasts, DVDs challenge Iran grip on TV|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/01/19/industry-us-iran-idUSTRE70I54420110119|publisher=Reuters|accessdate=22 April 2013|date=2011-01-19|archive-date=2013-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230231637/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/01/19/industry-us-iran-idUSTRE70I54420110119|dead-url=no}}</ref>

据法国《[[路透社|路透社]]》报道，伊朗的观众除了观看国家电视台认为合适的节目外，所能观看的选择很少。<ref name="reutersiran"/>因此韩剧在伊朗的收视率非常高，甚至高于在韩国的收视率，比如《[[朱蒙_(电视剧)|朱蒙]]》在伊朗的收视率达到80-90%而在韩国则是40%。《[[朱蒙_(电视剧)|朱蒙]]》男主角[[宋一国|宋一国]]也因此在伊朗成为超级明星。<ref name="songilgookiran">{{cite web|title=Song Il Gook is a superstar in Iran because of Jumong|url=http://www.allkpop.com/2009/08/song_il_gook_is_a_superstar_in_iran|publisher=Allkpop|accessdate=2013-04-21|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100401150243/http://www.allkpop.com/2009/08/song_il_gook_is_a_superstar_in_iran|archivedate=2010-04-01}}</ref>

